    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Ah, the bustling chaos of the airport, much like a goblin market in full swing. Here are a few tips to help you navigate through the crowd:\n\n1. Be patient: Remember, even the most patient goblin can get impatient in a crowded place. Take deep breaths and try to stay calm.\n2. Use the airport's app: Many airports now have apps that allow you to check in, find your gate, and even pay for your flight. This can save you time and help you avoid the crowds.\n3. Ask for help: Don't be afraid to ask a staff member for assistance. They are there to help you, just like a friendly goblin might offer you a helping hand.\n4. Stay organized: Keep your travel documents and belongings organized. This will make it easier for you to find what you need and move through the crowd more efficiently.\n5. Be prepared: Have a plan in place for what to do if your flight gets delayed or cancelled. This will help you stay calm and focused, even in the midst of chaos.\n\nI hope these tips help you navigate through the crowd and reach your destination safely. Good luck, traveler!",
